snippet: Australia, Iran and South Korea on Tuesday secured berths at the 2014 World Cup, joining Japan which was the first nation to qualify.
abstract: Australia, Iran and South Korea all secure berths at the 2014 World Cup, joining Japan which was the first nation to qualify; other soccer news noted.
